%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc06b95f-8449-4064-b66e-6dd56a568811%5C%22%3EFrom%20controversy%20to%20queen%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBosch's%20crowning%20comes%20after%20weeks%20of%20scandal%20surrounding%20the%20Miss%20Universe%20competition%2C%20which%20kicked%20off%20with%20a%20confrontation%20of%20her%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20November%204%2C%20the%20very%20first%20day%20of%20the%20pageant%2C%20Miss%20Thailand%20director%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiss-universe-director-nawat-itsaragrisil-miss-mexico-history-shaming-pageant-queens-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENawat%20Itsaragrisil%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20hosted%20Miss%20Universe%202025%2C%20got%20into%20an%20argument%20with%20Bosch%20over%20a%20sponsorship%20event.%20Their%20exchange%20was%20caught%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2Flive%2F%3Fref%3Dwatch_permalink%26v%3D824666627177997%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMiss%20Thailand%20Facebook%20livestream%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20quickly%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EItsaragrisil%20was%20criticizing%20the%20Miss%20Mexico%20team%20when%20he%20appeared%20to%20tell%20Bosch%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20listen%20to%20your%20director%2C%20you're%20a%20dumbhead.%26quot%3B%20Itsaragrisil%20later%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20word%20he%20had%20used%20was%20%26quot%3Bdamage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Bosch%20tried%20to%20speak%20up%2C%20Itsaragrisil%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20give%20you%20an%20opportunity%20to%20talk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20voice%2C%26quot%3B%20Bosch%20told%20him.%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20not%20respecting%20me%20as%20a%20woman.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222414%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Miss%20Mexico%20onstage%20in%20her%20evening%20gown%20during%20the%20Miss%20Universe%202025%20pageant%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3