090%5C%22%3EThe%20rigging%20allegations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223936%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Miss%20Venezuela%2C%20Miss%20Thailand%2C%20and%20Miss%20Mexico%20on%20the%20Miss%20Universe%20stage.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691fec0789026fbb4d0e1fbf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222624%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMiss%20Venezuela%2C%20Miss%20Thailand%2C%20and%20Miss%20Mexico%20were%20the%20top%20three%20at%20Miss%20Universe%202025.%3Cp%3ELILLIAN%20SUWANRUMPHA%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20days%20before%20the%20Miss%20Universe%20finals%2C%20composer%20Omar%20Harfouch%20also%20dropped%20out%20as%20a%20judge%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20organization%20had%20pre-selected%20the%20top%2030%20contestants%20through%20a%20%26quot%3Bsecret%20vote%26quot%3B%20that%20did%20not%20involve%20the%20official%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20honored%20to%20be%20invited%20as%20an%20official%20judge%2C%20and%20I%20approached%20it%20with%20full%20integrity%20and%20artistic%20dedication%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BBut%20that%20changed%20when%20I%20discovered%20the%20existence%20of%20a%20parallel%20selection%20committee%20acting%20independently%20from%20the%20official%20jury.%20That%20moment%20shifted%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20from%20trust%20to%20credibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDRNDIUxk6yQ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link%26igsh%3DYmhxbnh1dGdsaDBz%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%3C%2Fa%3E%20statement%20shared%20on%20November%2018%2C%20the%20Miss%20Universe%20Organization%20said%20Harfouch%20was%20confused%20by%20its%20use%20of%20a%20separate%20selection%20committee%20for%20the%20pageant's%20%26quot%3BBeyond%20the%20Crown%20Program%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20celebrates%20the%20contestants'%20charities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3