ber%2C%20and%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20Paramount's%20plans%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20about%201%2C000%20more%20cuts%20are%20coming%2C%20though%20the%20timeline%20on%20that%20is%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20analysts%20say%20a%20merger%20of%20Paramount%20and%20Warner%20Bros.%20would%20be%20challenging%20to%20get%20through%20in%20a%20normal%20regulatory%20environment%2C%20as%20a%20consolidated%20studio%20could%20potentially%20pay%20creatives%20less%20while%20raising%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAntitrust%20regulators%20typically%20focus%20on%20how%20a%20merger%20of%20two%20powerful%20companies%20could%20impact%20the%20labor%20market%20and%20their%20pricing%20power%20over%20consumers.%20However%2C%20Martin%2C%20the%20entertainment%20lawyer%2C%20said%20much%20of%20that%20conventional%20analysis%20%26quot%3Bis%20out%20the%20window%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20second%20Trump%20administration%2C%20in%20which%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-leaders-trump-relationship-tariffs-zuckerberg-musk-cook-pichai-altman-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonal%20relationships%3C%2Fa%3E%20play%20a%20larger%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20apparent%20goodwill%20toward%20Paramount%20and%20Ellison%2C%20along%20with%20his%20administration's%20M%26amp%3BA-friendly%20stance%2C%20has%20legal%20experts%20feeling%20rosy%20about%20the%20chances%20of%20Paramount's%20WBD%20bid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20room%20for%20some%20optimism%20by%20the%20companies%20that%20they%20would%20be%20able%20to%20consummate%20this%20merger%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ray%20Seilie%2C%20an%20entertainment%20litigator%20at%20Los-Angeles-based%20law%20firm%20Kinsella%20Holley%20Iser%20Kump%20Steinsapir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a5088956-210c-4a5b-bbee-10a29b1dc5e2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Now%20or%20never'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20WBD%20splits%20itself%20next%20summ