%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2025%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fdancing-with-the-stars-ratings-prince-night-semifinals-1236587456%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20TSA%20wants%20to%20charge%20flyers%20%2418%20if%20they%20show%20up%20at%20security%20without%20the%20right%20ID%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22TSA%20agent%20holding%20a%20real%20ID.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691fa05789026fbb4d0e1d85%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20TSA%20wants%20to%20charge%20flyers%20who%20don't%20have%20acceptable%20ID%20%2418%20to%20use%20biometric%20kiosks%20to%20verify%20their%20identity.%3Cp%3EJessica%20Christian%2FSan%20Francisco%20Chronicle%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20TSA%20proposed%20an%20%2418%20fee%20for%20travelers%20without%20acceptable%20ID%20at%20airport%20security%20checkpoints.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20fee%20aims%20to%20fund%20biometric%20kiosks%20to%20streamline%20identity%20verification%20and%20reduce%20delays.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20not%20a%20guarantee%20flyers%20clear%20security%2C%20and%20the%20%2418%20is%20non-refundable.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-id-requirements-airline-policies-tsa-delays-ticket-changes-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETransportation%20Security%20Administration%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20taken%20a%20page%20from%20the%20budget%20airline%20playbook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20filed%20a%20new%20proposal%20on%20Thursday%20that%20would%20charge%20travelers%20%2418%20at%20security%20checkpoints%20if%20they%20show%20up%20without%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-id-deadline-dmv-women-face-chaos-marriage-certificate-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EREAL%20ID%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20another%20acceptable%20government-issued%20ID%2C%20such%20as%20a%20passport%20or%20permanent%20resident%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fee%20covers%20the%20cost%20of%20creating%20and%20maintaining%20the%20new%20program%20and%20would%20essentially%20be%20required%20for%20an%20agent%20to%20access%20a%20biometric%20kiosk%20system%20designed%20to%20verify%20a%20traveler's%20identity%20more%20quickly%20than%20the%20current%20manual%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fee%20is%20optional%2C%20but%20flyers%20without%20acceptable%20ID%20risk%20not%20being%20allowed%20on%20their%20flight%20if%20they%20don't%20pay%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20when%20the%20rule%20to%20spur%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-id-everything-you-need-to-know-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EREAL%20ID%20adoption%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20go%20into%20effect.%20The%20filing%20said%20it'll%20begin%20when%20the%20agency%20opens%20registrations%20for%20the%20program%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20proposal%2C%20the%20%2418%20would%20be%20valid%20for%2010%20days%2C%20meaning%20travelers%20without%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-id-deadline-new-york-atlanta-airports-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompliant%20ID%20documents%3C%2Fa%3E%20wouldn't%20necessarily%20pay%20the%20fee%20every%20single%20trip%20within%20that%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TSA%20said%20the%20new%20technology%20would%20be%20less%20time%20and%20resource-intensive%20than%20the%20current%20process%20when%20a%20flyer%20lacks%20these%20IDs%2C%20which%20involves%20providing%20personal%20information%20or%20answering%20detailed%20questions%20to%20match%20flyers%20to%20government%20databases.%20They%20also%20face%20extra%20screening%20of%20their%20carry-ons%20and%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20added%20that%20the%20kiosks%20would%20just%20be%20an%20alternative%20attempt%20to%20verify%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-set-up-your-passport-in-apples-digital-id-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eflyer's%20identity%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20a%20guarantee.%20Those%20who%20can't%20clear%20airport%20security%20through%20any%20means%20would%20not%20be%20refunded%20the%20%2418.%20And%20they%20may%20still%20be%20subject%20to%20additional%20screening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TSA%20said%20the%20program%20would%20require%20spending%20on%20data%20infrastructure%2C%20software%20development%2C%20program%20management%2C%20and%20compliance.%20It%20added%20that%20it%20may%20impose%20a%20limit%20on%20how%20many%20times%20an%20individual%20could%20use%20the%20kiosk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20if%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-agents-receive-bonuses-working-during-shutdown-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETSA%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20be%20the%20ones%20to%20collect%20the%20fee%20when%20a%20flyer%20opts%20into%20the%20program.%20The%20TSA%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20question%20about%20where%20the%20fee%20will%20be%20paid%20and%20what%20payment%20types%20it%20will%20accept.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fee-based%20system%20would%20be%20separate%20from%20the%20TSA's%20existing%20use%20of%20facial%20recognition%20technology%2C%20which%20is%20already%20deployed%20voluntarily%20at%20dozens%20of%20airports%20nationwide%20%E2%80%94%20including%20major%20hubs%20like%20New%20York-JFK%2C%20Boston%20Logan%2C%20Denver%2C%20and%20Atlanta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20notice%20serves%20as%20a%20next%20step%20in%20the%20process%20in%20REAL%20ID%20compliance%2C%20which%20was%20signed%20into%20law%20more%20than%2020%20years%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20TSA%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Congress%20passed%20the%20REAL%20ID%20Act%20of%202005%20in%20response%20to%20the%209%2F11%20attacks%2C%20but%20it%20just%20rolled%20out%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20that%20additional%20guidance%20would%20come%20in%20th