nessinsider.com%2Fquit-dream-job-to-be-stay-at-home-dad-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estay-at-home%20dad%3C%2Fa%3E%20wasn't%20natural%20%E2%80%94%20not%20because%20of%20the%20dad%20part%2C%20but%20because%20I%20was%20often%20the%20only%20dad%20at%20the%20park%20or%20play%20group.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it%20gave%20me%20a%20rare%20chance%20to%20slow%20down.%20Danielle%2C%20who%20had%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freturning-to-work-from-a-career-break-what-i-learned-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereturn%20to%20corporate%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20that%20time%2C%20helped%20me%20realize%20I'd%20never%20really%20taken%20a%20step%20back%20to%20ask%20what%20I%20wanted%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20identity%20had%20been%20closely%20tied%20to%20my%20job%20for%20years.%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20that%20space%20would%20make%20room%20for%20a%20question%20that%20would%20change%20everything%3A%20%26quot%3BJeff%2C%20can%20you%20make%20me%20a%20bagel%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220fa93efd-aaa0-4e22-88b6-206d94303da2%5C%22%3EWhen%20you%20can't%20find%20the%20best%20bagel%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20go%20on%20coffee%20runs.%20Others%20go%20on%20Target%20runs%20or%20beer%20runs.%20For%20Danielle%20and%20me%2C%20it%20was%20always%20a%20weekly%20bagel%20run.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floved-miami-had-to-leave-for-small-florida-town-coast-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eliving%20in%20Central%20Florida%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20true%20bagel%20desert%20%E2%80%94%20meant%20driving%2045%20minutes%20to%20find%20a%20decent%20New%20York-style%20bagel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20my%20wife%20popped%20the%20question%2C%20given%20my%20newfound%20free%20time%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20try%20making%20her%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-brand-has-best-bagels-grocery-store-ranking%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eperfect%20bagel%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDanielle%20has%20vivid%20childhood%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fubreakifix-cofounder-jeffs-bagel-run-president-scaling-lessons-tech-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ememories%20of%20bagels%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20riding%20in%20her%20mom's%20station%20wagon%20on%20Long%20Island%2C%20eating%20one%20fresh%20from%20the%20bag.%20The%20best%20foods%2C%20of%20course%2C%20can%20transport%20us%20back%20to%20moments%20we%20just%20want%20to%20taste%20one%20more%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20was%2C%20I'd%20never%20baked%20anything%20in%20my%20life.%20I%20had%20zero%20culinary%20training.%20I%20just%20looked%20up%20the%20first%20recipe%20I%20could%20find%20and%20got%20to%20work.%20Those%20first%20bagels%20were%20terrible%20%E2%80%94%20dense%2C%20misshapen%2C%20and%20far%20from%20New%20York%20standards.%20But%20that%20only%20inspired%20me%20to%20try%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20day%2C%20Danielle%20would%20come%20home%20from%20work%20to%20a%20new%20batch%20waiting%20for%20her%20to%20critique.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20and%20my%20family%20was%20locked%20down%20with%20a%20mad%20bagel%20scientist.%20I'd%20make%20up%20to%20six%20dozen%20bagels%20a%20day.%20Bowls%20of%20dough%20covered%20the%20counters%2C%20each%20marked%20with%20recipe%20notes.%20My%20kids%20helped%20knead%20and%20mix%2C%20turning%20the%20kitchen%20into%20a%20full-on%20test%20lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDanielle%20would%20taste%20and%20review%20each%20one%20%E2%80%94%20the%20chewiness%2C%20the%20salt%2C%20the%20crust.%20Eventually%2C%20she%20joked%20that%20her%20work%20clothes%20might%20stop%20fitting%20if%20I%20didn't%20stop%20baking.%20So%2C%20we%20started%20giving%20them%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20box%20of%20Jeff's%20Bagel%20Run%20bagels.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e8e83abd5e944effb1939%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20he%20was%20getting%20started%2C%20Perera%20would%20make%20up%20to%20six%20dozen%20bagels%20per%20day%2C%20determined%20to%20get%20it%20right%2C%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Jeff's%20Bagel%20Run%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2243b0eaa1-7235-4beb-aa76-6b4f8e4329e6%5C%22%3EGetting%20it%20right%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20look%20on%20my%20wife's%20face%20when%20I%20finally%20nailed%20the%20perfect%20bagel%20was%20unforgettable.%20We%20looked%20at%20each%20other%20and%20asked%3A%20Could%20we%20actually%20sell%20these%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20made%20a%20simple%20flyer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhusband-wife-built-million-dollar-cinnamon-bun-business-instagram-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eposted%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20sold%20a%20few%20dozen.%20One%20of%20our%20early%20customers%20was%20a%20local%20journalist%20who%20wrote%20about%20us%2C%20and%20suddenly%20we%20had%20more%20orders%20than%20we%20could%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20kitchen%20exploded%20into%20a%20full-scale%20operation.%20We%20had%20five%20refrigerators%20stretching%20into%20the%20garage%2C%20extension%20cords%20running%20everywhere%2C%20and%20breakers%20popping%20constantly.%20We%20upgraded%20our%20confection%20ovens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20third%20week%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20started%20posting%20our%20bagel%20menu.%20Our%20bagels%20were%20selling%20out%20in%20seconds.%20During%20one%20stretch%2C%20we%20baked%20for%2027%20days%20straight.%20I%20delivered%20bagels%20across%20town%2C%20spreading%20a%20little%20joy%20during%20lockdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2291dc775d-7baa-4124-b23b-14a1818851a0%5C%22%3EScaling%20up%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20we%20did%20our%20first%20in-person%20market.%20People%20lined%20up%20for%20a%20block%20to%20buy%20bagels.%20The%20next%20year%2C%20a%20downpour%20hit%20mid-market%2C%20and%20every%20other%20vendor%20packed%20up.%20But%20our%20line%20stayed.%20We%20threw%20tarps%20over%20the%20bagels%2C%20and%20people%20showed%20up%20soaked%20to%20buy%20half%20a%20dozen.%20That's%20when%20we%20knew%20we%20had%20something%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20sold%20our%20house%20and%20launched%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-day-workweek-kickstarter-great-productivity-social-life-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKickstarter%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20%2410%2C000%20goal.%20We%20raised%20over%20%2422%2C000%20from%20276%20backers%2C%20enough%20to%20buy%20equipment%20and%20take%20the%20next%20step.%20Danielle%20quit%20her%20job%2C%20and%20together%20we%20opened%20our%20first%20store%20in%20Ocoee%2C%20Florida%2C%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Jeff's%20Bagel%20Run%20%E2%80%94%20named%20after%20our%20weekly%20drives%20to%20find%20the%20best%20bagels%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20growing%20franchise%20with%20more%20than%20100%20stores%20in%20six%20states%2C%20and%20counting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221911%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Danielle%20Perera%20is%20the%20cofounder%20of%20Jeff's%20Bagel%20Run%20in%20Florida.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e8db9e1a9cbb014de93a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221434%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDanielle%20Perera%20grew%20up%20in%20Long%20Island%2C%20New%20York%2C%20and%20wanted%20to%20find%20the%20perfect%20bagel%20in%20Florida.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Jeff's%20Bagel%20Run%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e5d1c182-61f4-410f-b535-4c632f05f348%5C%22%3EPeace%2C%20love%2C%20and%20bagels%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconfessions-of-a-startup-founder-wife-marriage-tiktok-games-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebusiness%20with%20your%20spouse%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecan%20be%20tough.%20We%20make%20it%20work%20by%20having%20short%20memories%3B%20what%20happens%20at%20work%20stays%20at%