n%20toured%20the%20US%20in%202018%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaudi-arabia-crown-prince-mohammed-bin-salman-us-trip-meetings-2018-3%23bill-clinton-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerica's%20mogul%20class%20clamored%20for%20an%20audience%3C%2Fa%3E.%20More%20recently%2C%20American%20business%20leaders%20have%20been%20showing%20up%20at%20Saudi-run%20business%20conferences%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-saudi-arabia-investment-conference-business-tech-leaders-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflying%20out%20to%20the%20desert%20to%20attend%20high-profile%20events%20alongside%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-house-dinner-saudi-prince-business-execs-ceos-musk-su-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epacking%20the%20White%20House%20for%20this%20week's%20events%20feting%20bin%20Salman%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20time%20American%20interest%20in%20oil%20money%20has%20flagged%20was%20after%20October%202018%2C%20after%20the%20murder%20and%20dismemberment%20of%20Washington%20Post%20contributor%20Jamal%20Khashoggi%20%E2%80%94%20a%20shocking%20act%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcia-assessment-mohammed-bin-salman-khashoggi-murder-trump-russia-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20CIA%20concluded%20was%20ordered%20by%20bin%20Salman%20himself%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20the%20fallout%20of%20Khashoggi's%20death%2C%20many%20American%20firms%20scrambled%20to%20distance%20themselves%20from%20Saudi%20money%3B%20Ari%20Emanuel%2C%20the%20high-profile%20Hollywood%20agent%2C%20made%20a%20point%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F03%2F08%2Fbusiness%2Fendeavor-saudi-arabia.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereturning%20a%20%24400%20million%20investment%20the%20country%20had%20made%20in%20his%20Endeavor%20agency%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20within%20a%20few%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaudi-arabia-qatar-uae-investment-hollywood-media-entertainment-mbs-khashoggi-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmericans%20were%20open%20to%20doing%20business%20with%20the%20kingdom%20again%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20fact%2C%20many%20media%20and%20tech%20leaders%20say%2C%20they%20have%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20work%20with%20the%20Saudis%20and%20other%20petrostates%20%E2%80%94%20because%20that's%20where%20the%20money%20is.%20And%20now%20the%20Trump%20administration%20is%20actively%20courting%20oil%20money%20%E2%80%94%20and%20bristling%20at%20suggestions%20that%20Kashoggi's%20death%20is%20a%20reason%20not%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn0gdkwp2p9o%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThings%20happen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20told%20reporters%20this%20week%2C%20while%20continuing%20to%20insist%20that%20bin%20Salman%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20murder.%20%26quot%3BHe%20knew%20nothing%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20oil%20money%20does%20end%20up%20financing%20a%20Paramount%20bid%20for%20WBD%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20the%20first%20time%20we've%20seen%20foreign%20money%20in%20American%20media.%20Australian-born%20Rupert%20Murdoch%20became%20a%20US%20citizen%20specifically%20so%20he%20could%20build%20Fox%20in%20the%201980s.%20Japan's%20Sony%20has%20been%20in%20Hollywood%20since%201989%2C%20when%20it%20bought%20what%20was%20then%20called%20Columbia%20Pictures.%20French%20conglomerate%20Vivendi%20used%20to%20own%20Universal%20Studios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20you%20want%20to%2C%20you%20can%20shrug%20and%20say%20that%20money%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20or%20Qatar%2C%20or%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20is%20nothing%20new%20%E2%80%94%20money%20is%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20money%20is%20trickier%20to%20accept%20than%20other%20money.%20See%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20recent%20flare-up%20when%20a%20group%20of%20high-profile%20comedians%20accepted%20outsize%20checks%20to%20perform%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fculture%2F464429%2Friyadh-comedy-festival-saudi-arabia-bill-burr-marc-maron%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESaudi-sponsored%20festival%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20it's%20certainly%20worth%20wondering%20what%20oil%20money%20might%20mean%20in%20a%20media%20company%20that%20makes%20movies%2C%20TV%20shows%2C%20and%20runs%20multiple%20news%20outlets%20%E2%80%94%20like%20a%20combined%20Paramount-WBD.%20Would%20there%20be%20pressure%20%E2%80%94%20explicit%20or%20implicit%20%E2%80%94%20to%20create%20content%20that's%20more%20acceptable%20to%20the%20country%20writing%20the%20checks%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20know.%20But%20we%20do%20know%20that%20they%20can%20afford%20it%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20today's%20political%20climate%20suggests%20they%20might%20be%20able%20to%20pull%20it%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaudi-arabia-paramount-warner-bros-discovery-ellison-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763673879000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691f8658abd5e944effb2ffc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaudi-arabia-paramount-warner-bros-discovery-ellison-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20hard%20to%20imagine%20Saudi%20Arabia%20%E2%80%94%20or%20any%20Gulf%20state%20%E2%80%94%20owning%20a%20piece%20of%20a%20US%20media%20giant.%20Now%2C%20it%20might%20happen.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pkafka%40insider.com%20(Peter%20Kafka)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A75%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaudi-arabia-paramount-warner-bros-discovery-ellison-2025-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Sed