resilience%2C%20showed%20promising%20results%20in%20increasing%20essential%20nutrient%20levels%20by%20up%20to%2080%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20introducing%20zinc%20soil%20bacteria%20to%20enrich%20the%20soil%20ecosystem%2C%20the%20seeds%20enabled%20plants%20to%20absorb%20more%20nutrients%2C%20ultimately%20leading%20to%20significantly%20higher%20nutritional%20content%20in%20the%20harvested%20crops%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22By%20encouraging%20the%20shift%20from%20traditional%20seeds%20to%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20enhanced%20their%20income%20as%20well.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364813%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20By%20encouraging%20the%20shift%20from%20traditional%20seeds%20to%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20enhanced%20their%20income%20as%20well.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20further%2C%20Prateek%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20we%20found%20that%20the%20baseline%20levels%20of%20zinc%20in%20the%20traditional%20variety%20of%20wheat%20is%20around%2028%20parts%20per%2